<H3> <TI>   Matra Achieves 50-Percent Growth in Asia </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94WS0128C Paris PRODUCTIQUE/AFFAIRES in French 20 Nov 93 pp 
5-6 </F>

<F P=103> 94WS0128C </F>
