<ABS>  Europe/International </ABS>
<DATE1>   9 March 1994 </DATE1>
<F P=100> WEST EUROPE </F>
<F P=101> FACTORY AUTOMATION, ROBOTICS </F>
<H3> <TI>   ABB Launches Two Robots </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94WS0175C Paris PRODUCTIQUE/AFFAIRES in French 30 Dec 93 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 94WS0175C </F>
